{"tid":888601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突然發現有個好地方去發洩大家壓力既好地方","createTime":"2018-11-04T01:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T02:29:13.000Z","uid":60150,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4441d2bda618967009aefbf3e3a2de49b7eb40cd","tid":888601,"uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"呢幾年咪有d 健身美容狗係街度騷擾人既<br />\n好多人驚到唔想理佢地或者無視了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實諗深一層, 只要惡過佢地, 就冇事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且可以將大家平時既怨氣一次過發出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平衡身心健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地做緊野, 要搵食, 如果你地夾埋浪費佢地時間, 佢地反而會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我決定只要佢地埋身, 就帶定粗口紙鬧到佢地祖宗十八代<br />\n大家一唔開心, 千祈唔好去和富商業中心搵佢地出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb83674552fa51463ff3a174070ea8e704b61f8","tid":888601,"uid":163500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"你有壓力我有壓力<br />\n何必搵人出氣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:無野做失業緊"},{"pid":"b487aaa616e3c448249fa9782e965afd024251ae","tid":888601,"uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb83674552fa51463ff3a174070ea8e704b61f8","tid":888601,"uid":163500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"你有壓力我有壓力<br />\n何必搵人出氣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:無野做失業緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"你應該冇俾呢d健身狗或者美容狗煩過<br />\n佢地係會擋係你面前, 煩到你咩心情都冇哂<br />\n<br />\n我反而諗起, 咁如果大家唔開心, 或者有咩睇唔開<br />\n就搵下呢d咁積極同人交流既朋友傾計啦係咪先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08338b5e42af8b0dd29f1d3b44a99cd2aff79e1f","tid":888601,"uid":41174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:22:39.000Z","msg":"有次行過信和<br />\n話左唔得閒都仲要追我到街尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話派多張放飯<br />\n屌你老母健身狗<br />\n我轉頭返信和佢仲派緊<br />\n說好的食飯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058cea23e982e0c967bd35928aece943fa06e836","tid":888601,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbb83674552fa51463ff3a174070ea8e704b61f8","tid":888601,"uid":163500,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"你有壓力我有壓力<br />\n何必搵人出氣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:無野做失業緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T02:29:13.000Z","msg":"你條死毒撚唔岀街識條撚咩"}]}